        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-300">
          We're here to help you plan your financial future. Let us create a map
          with easy to take steps, AI-powered tips and evaluations of your
          progress. We're homegrown Canadian and we'll teach you how to maximize
          our Canadian savings plans and taxation systems.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-10 flex items-center justify-center gap-x-6">
          <a
            href="https://app.foos.ca/try"
            class="rounded-md bg-indigo-500 px-3.5 py-1.5 text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-indigo-400 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-indigo-400"
          >
            Get started
          </a>
          <a
            href="#pricing"
            class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-white"
          >
            Learn more
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <img
        src="/planner.png"
        alt="App screenshot"
        width="2432"
        height="1442"
        class="mt-16 rounded-md bg-white/5 shadow-2xl ring-1 ring-white/10 sm:mt-24"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="pricing">
