              >
                <ArrowTrendingUpIcon className="h-6 w-6 text-white" />
              </div>
              Contributions
            </dt>
            <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">
              Set your contributions that you're planning on making each year.
              We'll help you with guidelines and rules to optimize your savings.
            </dd>
          </div>

          <div class="relative pl-16">
            <dt class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-gray-900">
              <div
                class="absolute top-0 left-0 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-indigo-600"
              >
                <ArrowTrendingDownIcon className="h-6 w-6 text-white" />
              </div>
              Withdrawals
            </dt>
            <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">
              Once you're into retirement, you'll need to start withdrawing
              money from your accounts. We'll help you get the most out of your
              savings.
            </dd>
          </div>

          <div class="relative pl-16">
            <dt class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-gray-900">
              <div
                class="absolute top-0 left-0 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-indigo-600"
              >
                <BuildingLibraryIcon className="h-6 w-6 text-white" />
              </div>
              Taxes
            </dt>
            <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">
              We'll estimate your taxes each year and help you optimize them. It
              gets even better with a partner, with our family plan you can
              optimize your incomes together. Income splitting gives you the
              most tax efficient plan.
            </dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

