            </dt>
            <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">
              Every year we'll let you know how you did against your goals for
              that year and help you set more accurate goals for next year.
              We'll learn to work with each other better as the years go by.
            </dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-yellow-200" id="faq">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl py-24 px-6 sm:py-32 lg:px-8">
